* Desmonus sighed as he feet toughed Alliance ground, brushing ash from her 
shaply armor.
She had missed her meal and she was hungry again, getting away from that 
battle had spent what energy she had sucked from Bloodystrike and Reptilica. 
She needed to replenish herself again.
Shaking herself, Desmonus set to work on straightening her plates when a few 
voices cought her attention, looking over towards a group of bots gathered 
arounf Perndabot and some new guy.
She straightened her last plate and then wandered over to the group, 
standing beside one large gustalt leg, listening to what they were all 
saying.*
